Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:25.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:32.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先於Frontier數年啟航的21號巨型移民船團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由大企業設計制定方案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:38.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無保留地投入各種先進技術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:42.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航海過程中也繼續發展技術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:46.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電腦工程學和植入技術上成果卓越
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:50.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一躍成為少數擁有高科技能力的船團之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使是Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Vajra的攻擊下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:58.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求援 求援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些臭蟲們爬上了主島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:13.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船體各部件無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:15.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,De-fold成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:20.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認本艦前方02方位達爾特弗和卡利托斯的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:21.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:25.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:29.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 我們的首要任務雖然是救援倖存艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:32.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其同等 甚至更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:36.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集Vajra的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不代表新統合軍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是大總統閣下的要求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以這樣理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:49.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:53.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會留意的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:56.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 投入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:45.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M5和6 M5…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾特沒來？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到我的告別演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間雖然短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很慶幸能認識Frontier的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生許多事 讓大家操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚像平常那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飆出Macross的速度來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髏隊長向各機通話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是給軍隊打頭陣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便還要收集Vajra的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試作型空間跳躍通信誘導系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態良好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有它應該不會再被Vajra擾亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:01.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有亞爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你盡可能靠後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:13.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先跟上我再說 不許走遠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機 Planet Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 路哈尼 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:22.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步 米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別又因為看不見我就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真多嘴 葛蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的事糾纏不休
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:54.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼笨重的重裝型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能被它甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:46.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡納莉亞 乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:07.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dabind01向達爾特弗通話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借甲板一用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是達爾特弗 請腳下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.16,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs44}Konig Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(635,655)}怪獸之王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主甲板固定 抗衝擊防護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dabind01開始迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的人都撤出我的視野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konig Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物退散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:52.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:57.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆 先保護損傷嚴重的卡利托斯撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認與Frontier空間跳躍數據鏈接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間跳躍通信 數據鏈接狀態良好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延遲為+40
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:16.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一攻擊部隊 開始與Vajra交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.45,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs44}Hyperion&Prometheus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(512,655)}土衛七
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(730,655)}土衛十六
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二攻擊隊正在部署中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯 受損率45%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負傷者眾多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先派遣救援部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕的切換不好 查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佔優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似比想像的優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:46.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:52.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 又到線路上偷聽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 幾乎是現場直播
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾特 怎麼還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼精彩的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:17.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:25.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實應該親口告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些難以啟齒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作原因 今天回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定會遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那亞爾特也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:50.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的那位飛行員似乎也很賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:52.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心的是Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且飛行員的工作如果是戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作就是唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯 正撤離戰鬥區域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離空間跳躍安全範圍還有450
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種空間斷層的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能更早逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:47.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯被炸沉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖存者…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:57.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徑直穿越了空間斷層
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra的戰艦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太靠前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:20.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必須對它…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束發射器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這種空間跳躍能量反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是空間跳躍牽引器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 丟失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:43.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-1 發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:45.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路卡被敵人吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擊落了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:48.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船俘虜併吞掉了路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到最後一首了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必須和大家告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然時間過得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:24.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻留下了美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在廣闊的銀河中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能不能重逢
