Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐明知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:54.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道…卻
